this_title: Fast Cars and Superstars: The Gillette Young Guns Celebrity Race
introduction: Twelve celebrites, including Jewel, Tony Hawk, Serena Williams and William Shatner, will be paired with six young stock-car racers who will train them how to race. The seven-episode series will culminate in a head-to-head celebrity race-off with each young driver coaching a celeb from the pit.
